'''Lagayan''' is a 6th class [[Philippine municipality|municipality]] in the [[Philippine province|province]] of [[Abra province|Abra]], [[Philippines]]. According to the [[2000]] census, it has a population of 3,894 people in 796 households.

==Deng Barangay==

Ing Lagayan atin yang 5 [[barangay]].

* Ba-i
* Collago
* Pang-ot
* Poblacion
* Pulot

